code: @Override public void accept(Iterable<TriggerEvent> events) {     try {         executionService.processEventsAsync(events).     } catch (Exception e) {         logger.error((Supplier<?>) () -> new ParameterizedMessage("failed to process triggered events [{}]", (Object) stream(events.spliterator(), false).toArray(size -> new TriggerEvent[size])), e).     } }
